Normally in entity we will maintain only the Relationship and the fields. The Autowired and other business logic should be maitained in the service class. 

Dont use these Autowire in entity class, so because of using it - its considering those as a column / field. Becuase Autowired are maintained by SpringIOC and entity are used to manage the db related operations. Ref : https://stackoverflow.com/questions/54014047/can-we-use-autowired-on-an-entity-object-in-spring#:~:text=You%20can%20only%20autowire%20only,%40Service%20%2C%20%40Repository%20etc.

